        <heading>3248.  Enforcement of conventional mortgage or pledge</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3248.  Enforcement of conventional mortgage or pledge
The provisions of Articles 3246 and 3247 shall not prevent the enforcement of a conventional mortgage on or a pledge of movable or immovable property of the succession in a separate proceeding.</p>
        </content>
